    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Points on the earth characterized by coordinates that are determined by observation of celestial bodies. The expression is usually used in connection with positions on land determined with great accuracy for survey purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
